      <a class="btn" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jide-ogunyemi-014b3133a?utm_source=share&utm_campaign=share_via&utm_content=profile&utm_medium=android_app" target="_blank"> Let's connect and talk!</a>
      <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1KQQ1YDIXr5ZNb1Q2a0mh8sXXC-lNesllJd3g2EbbEcg/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline ml-5">
